{"tid":2140660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大︰武肺可上腦 致神經失常","createTime":"2020-08-05T06:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T14:59:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8408445846495548e3a2176e9449af2b8b876a45","tid":2140660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:53:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/7N4CPBGWJLDQPADAP6FIHOJ3AI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2F7N4CPBGWJLDQPADAP6FIHOJ3AI%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeasg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=37125c00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2F7N4CPBGWJLDQPADAP6FIHOJ3AI%2F&h=9629849d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/7N4CPBGWJLDQPADAP6FIHOJ3AI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港大︰武肺可上腦 致神經失常<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fQzSRC2aI-qeBnfm2_rdYGKG5gE=/921x590/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CGLSC5PZPJZJ6A3E6CJ2HUA3CA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfQzSRC2aI-qeBnfm2_rdYGKG5gE%3D%2F921x590%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCGLSC5PZPJZJ6A3E6CJ2HUA3CA.jpg&h=cd52d896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔繁毅表示，研究結果解釋了部份受感染病人失去味覺及嗅覺，可能與神經細胞受感染有關。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港大醫學院與內地一項聯合研究發現，武肺病毒可以「上腦」，感染人類的腦部、神經祖細胞（即比較年幼的神經細胞），引起呼吸道感染以外的其他症狀，包括頭痛、失去味覺、嗅覺，甚至神經失常。<br />\n<br />\n研究結果於生命科學期刊《細胞研究》（《Cell Research》）發表，文章指出，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勁過沙士 可感染神經祖細胞<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：先遣隊訪實驗室 工業園員工抗議<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，武肺病毒可以有效感。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n領導研究的港大醫學院生物醫學學。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他補充，2015年再次出現的寨卡病毒，也被指能破壞人腦中的神經祖細胞，導致患者小頭畸形、嚴重的發育缺陷及成人的其他神經系統異常。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，研究團隊建議，現時需要密切監測人類感染病毒後，併發中樞神經系統問題的慢性或長期性後果。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。由於本港病人能及早接受治療，患上病毒上腦等腦部併發症的情況相對較少。"},{"pid":"bc76f3e9ef5645cee22b88a47cb88edb3ca2ac21","tid":2140660,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"兒登熱狗:Just Flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10895ea6d8a862c8af16cfecaad3ef0ba03fc93","tid":2140660,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1eb16a86b69fbf1699314e2a3eeb339c7ab3083","tid":2140660,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"本身中武肺嘅多數係藍屍<br />\n不過佢哋本身都神經失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0964f82dba4438f376a1005f809d1be1012e33c6","tid":2140660,"uid":130044,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"終於解釋到班官點解咁撚柒同on9"},{"pid":"69d50318508d40f2940ead747d7dfe9b7e42f532","tid":2140660,"uid":255980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1eb16a86b69fbf1699314e2a3eeb339c7ab3083","tid":2140660,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"本身中武肺嘅多數係藍屍<br />\n不過佢哋本身都神經失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:56:42.000Z","msg":"負負得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af1612fddfde2def64d997c41ffbd5a5aff4195","tid":2140660,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"到底藍絲神經失常先中武肺定中左武肺先神經失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728bdc9b72467561ebfc6a5b939d5796c0b94fe7","tid":2140660,"uid":286038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T06:57:28.000